$55

AND

$86

, OF WHICH

$44

AND

$0

WERE DETERMINED TO BE IMPAIRED. WE RECORDED NO ALLOWANCE FOR LOSSES ON THESE IMPAIRED RECEIVABLES AS THE COLLATERAL VALUES EXCEEDED THE CARRYING VALUES OF THE RECEIVABLES.

INCOME RECOGNITION IS GENERALLY SUSPENDED FOR FINANCING RECEIVABLES AT THE DATE FULL RECOVERY OF INCOME AND PRINCIPAL BECOMES NOT PROBABLE. INCOME IS RECOGNIZED WHEN FINANCING RECEIVABLES BECOME CONTRACTUALLY CURRENT AND PERFORMANCE IS DEMONSTRATED BY THE CUSTOMER.

