OF RECEIVABLES RELATED TO INDEMNIFICATIONS FROM SPIRIT AEROSYSTEMS, INC. (SPIRIT), FOR COSTS INCURRED RELATED TO PENSION AND RETIREE MEDICAL OBLIGATIONS OF FORMER BOEING EMPLOYEES THAT WERE SUBSEQUENTLY EMPLOYED BY SPIRIT. DURING THE FOURTH QUARTER OF 2014, BOEING FILED A COMPLAINT AGAINST SPIRIT IN DELAWARE SUPERIOR COURT SEEKING TO ENFORCE OUR RIGHTS TO INDEMNIFICATION AND TO RECOVER FROM SPIRIT AMOUNTS INCURRED BY BOEING FOR PENSION AND RETIREE MEDICAL OBLIGATIONS. WE EXPECT TO FULLY RECOVER FROM SPIRIT.

